    </profile>
    <profile name="Democracy Protects" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="19c9-8e91-824c-1d3d">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">While this model is within range of an objective marker you control, this model has the [Feel No Pain 4+] ability.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Flames of Democracy" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="ce2b-1a10-572f-40d8">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">In your Shooting phase, after this model has shot, you can select one enemy INFANTRY or MONSTER unit hit by one or more of those attacks made with a [TORRENT] weapon. That enemy unit must take a Battle-shock test, subtracting 2 from that test.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Helldiver" typeId="c547-1836-d8a-ff4f" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="6cb0-3515-1eec-8391">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="M" typeId="e703-ecb6-5ce7-aec1">6&quot;</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="T" typeId="d29d-cf75-fc2d-34a4">5</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="SV" typeId="450-a17e-9d5e-29da">3+</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="W" typeId="750a-a2ec-90d3-21fe">4</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="LD" typeId="58d2-b879-49c7-43bc">4+</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="OC" typeId="bef7-942a-1a23-59f8">3</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Damaged: 1-3 Wounds Remaining" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="2a62-209e-97e3-6765">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">While this model has 1-3 wounds remaining, each time this model makes an attack, subtract 1 from the Hit roll.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
      <comment>1-3</comment>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Crewed Transport" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="d8b9-a87a-9ef2-b4e6">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">This model has the transport capacity of 1 HELLDIVER model. While this model has no HELLDIVER models inside of it, this model is unable to perform any movement, attacks, or charges.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Sentry Fortification" typeId="9cc3-6d83-4dd3-9b64" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="218e-dcbe-bb56-22e1">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">While an enemy unit is only within Engagement Range of one or more FORTIFICATIONS from your army:
■That unit can still be selected as the target of ranged attacks, but each time such an attack is made, unless it is made with a Pistol, subtract 1 from the Hit roll.
■Models in that unit do not need to take Desperate Escape tests due to Falling Back while Battle-shocked, except for those that will move over enemy models when doing so.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Sentry" typeId="c547-1836-d8a-ff4f" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="9ada-7844-8db2-abf6">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="M" typeId="e703-ecb6-5ce7-aec1">-</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="T" typeId="d29d-cf75-fc2d-34a4">5</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="SV" typeId="450-a17e-9d5e-29da">4+</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="W" typeId="750a-a2ec-90d3-21fe">4</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="LD" typeId="58d2-b879-49c7-43bc">9+</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="OC" typeId="bef7-942a-1a23-59f8">1</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
  </sharedProfiles>
  <sharedRules>
    <rule name="Special" id="4434-2f46-a3c3-5faa" hidden="false">
      <description>Weapons with the keyword [SPECIAL] in their profile can only be used if the wielding model was not reinforced in the same turn.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Rapid Reinforcement" id="d10f-febb-6d48-7c67" hidden="false">
      <description>In the Reinforcements step of your Movement phase if there is less than 4 friendly HELLDIVER units on the battlefield, you may set up a HELLDIVER unit from your Strategic Reserves anywhere on the battlefield that is wholly within 10&quot; of a friendly HELLDIVER model within that model&apos;s line of sight and more than 3&quot; away from all enemy models.

If there are no friendly HELLDIVER models currently on the battlefield, you must instead set this unit up wholly within your deployment zone and more than 6&quot; away from all enemy models.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Only Whats Needed" id="f384-9c36-0de9-c360" hidden="false">
      <description>During the Declare Battle Formations step, you can assign any number of HELLDIVER or SUPPORT STRATAGEM units from your army list to your Strategic Reserves. Your army can never include more than 4 HELLDIVER units on the battlefield at the same time. You cannot place any SUPPORT STRATAGEMS during the Deploy Armies step.</description>
    </rule>
    <rule name="Request Equipment" id="739a-308b-ed12-0538" hidden="false">
      <description>You always have access to the SUPPORT STRATAGEM stratagem.
Before the beginning of the battle, choose 4 stratagems that are either EAGLE, ORBITAL, or SUPPORT stratagems, you would have access to these stratagems until the end of battle.</description>
    </rule>
  </sharedRules>
