          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">Once per battle, in your Shooting phase, you can use this ability. If you do, for each unit within 9&quot; of this model (including this model&apos;s unit), roll a number of D6 equal to the combined Wounds characteristics of all models currently in that unit. For each 4+, that unit suffers 2 mortal wounds.</characteristic>
