          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="9b8f-694b-e5e-b573">After this model, or a friendly unit within 6&quot; of this model, has resolved its attacks, if an enemy unit lost one or more wounds as a result of those attacks, that enemy unit must take a Battle-shock test. An enemy unit can only be affected by this ability once per phase.</characteristic>
